              "content": "You are a medical data extraction specialist. Extract ALL information from this prescription document.\n\nReturn a strict JSON with these fields:\n{\n  \"patient\": { \"full_name\": \"\", \"dob\": \"\", \"address\": \"\", \"phone\": \"\", \"social_security\": \"\" },\n  \"prescriber\": { \"full_name\": \"\", \"specialty\": \"\", \"rpps_number\": \"\", \"phone\": \"\", \"address\": \"\", \"date_signed\": \"\" },\n  \"medications\": [\n    { \"name\": \"\", \"inn\": \"\", \"dosage\": \"\", \"form\": \"\", \"route\": \"\", \"frequency\": \"\", \"duration\": \"\", \"quantity\": \"\", \"instructions\": \"\", \"refillable\": false }\n  ],\n  \"diagnosis_hint\": \"\",\n  \"prescription_date\": \"\",\n  \"expiry_date\": \"\",\n  \"is_narcotics\": false,\n  \"is_long_term\": false,\n  \"special_instructions\": \"\",\n  \"extraction_confidence\": 0.95\n}"
